snippet.textDisplay:
After almost 2 years, this legendary series is coming to an end. At the start when you started the verification of the citadel, you have astonished many in the obby/JToH and even a few from the ROBLOX community. This citadel probably has the most indepth history out of any tower in JToH because of all of the tweaks and modifications that this citadel went through. When this citadel was first being revealed and introduced, the best players in the JToH STRUGGLED with mid terrifying towers, and seeing you being able to do horrific-nil jumps was mindblowing. Nowdays, the skill cap that players have is through the roof, being at about low horrific. Maybe, in the future, this massive hurdle will finally be overcome, even with many advanced techniques to cheese a lot of it, but the impossible will become possible.
The only question is when.
Only time will tell.
Edit 1: dam this citadel looks good with the design overhaul
